# KI Risiko – Executive Summaries (LLM via GenAI-Nexus Azure-style)
# MAX RECALL VERSION: NO FILTERING / NO REJECTIONS
#
# Reads:  C:\Users\SHTANDO\Desktop\KI Risko\Analyse_Tabelle\analyse_tabelle_<rohst>.csv
